---

<section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-background">
        <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
        <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container hero-container-grid">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <div class="badge fade-up">Alto Padr√£o & Convers√£o</div>
            <h1 class="fade-up delay-1">Cria√ß√£o de Sites de <span class="text-primary">Impacto</span><br>para escalar seu neg√≥cio.</h1>
            <p class="fade-up delay-2">N√£o √© apenas um site. √â a sua autoridade digital materializada em design premium e estrat√©gia de vendas.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta fade-up delay-3">
                <Button href="/planos" size="lg" variant="primary">Ver Planos Exclusivos</Button>
                <Button href="#projects" variant="outline" size="lg">Conhecer Portf√≥lio</Button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-visual fade-in delay-3">
            <div class="glass-panel">
                <div class="chart-slider">
                    <!-- Slide 1: Growth Line Chart -->
                    <div class="slide active">
                        <div class="chart-content">
                            <h3><span class="icon">üìà</span> Crescimento Prev√≠sivel</h3>
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 300 200" class="chart-svg">
                                <defs>
                                    <linearGradient id="chartGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
